<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="321" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,151,824]" pageId="5" pageNumber="321">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,727,752]" pageId="5" pageNumber="321">Comments.</emphasis>
This species is distinguished by the prescutellar furrow with five cross carinae, smooth vertex with granulose face, and the sinuose anterior transverse groove of metasoma.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
